$WmMPID_リリス,ch05_53_Lilith_F_Normal,Face|Corrin... Even though I can't tell you
the truth, I will always protect you...$k$p$Sbs1000|

$WmMEID_スカビオサ,ch00_24_Scabiosa_F_Normal,Face|We've arrived.$k$pSo, this is Midgard, then...the human
realm. And I suppose we're in the
Kingdom of Askr now.$k$p$WmMEID_プルメリア,ch00_25_Plumeria_F_Normal,Face_Pain|This is where they commit all their
obscene human acts... How vile.$k$p$EFace|...Nothing to be done but carry out
Lady Freyja's orders and return to
Dökkálfheimr as quickly as possible.$k$p$WmMEID_スカビオサ,ch00_24_Scabiosa_F_Normal,Face|Indeed.$k$p$WmMEID_プルメリア,ch00_25_Plumeria_F_Normal,Face_Pain|If these wretched creatures somehow
manage to stop us... We can't allow it.
The things they're capable of...$k$pI shudder at the thought of them
even getting nea—$k$p$EFace|...Hm.$k$p$WmMEID_スカビオサ,ch00_24_Scabiosa_F_Normal,Face|Is something wrong?$k$p$WmMEID_プルメリア,ch00_25_Plumeria_F_Normal,Face|...No, it's nothing. I just...$k$pThe landscape...feels somehow
familiar. It must be déjà vu...$k$pI just have the feeling I've been
here before...$k$p$WmMEID_スカビオサ,ch00_24_Scabiosa_F_Normal,Face|...Yes.$k$pThat is strange. I feel the same...
But I don't know why.$k$p$WmMEID_プルメリア,ch00_25_Plumeria_F_Normal,Face|No use wasting time thinking about it.
We are dökkálfar of Dökkálfheimr.
Midgard has polluted our senses.$k$p$WmMEID_スカビオサ,ch00_24_Scabiosa_F_Normal,Face|You're right. Let's go, then. We must
see Lady Freyja's orders through...$k$p$Sbs150|
